<view class="app-page no-bottom with-sticky">
<view class="status-space"></view>
<view class="page-titlebar"><navigator class="back-btn" url="/pages/merchant-design/publish/publish"><image class="icon" mode="aspectFit" src="/assets/icons/back.svg" /></navigator><view class="title-block"><view class="page-title">商品图片</view><view class="page-subtitle">主图、详情图、产地图，统一用于商品发布</view></view></view>
<view class="photo-strip"><view class="photo-thumb"><image mode="aspectFill" src="/assets/goods/g2.svg" /><text class="mini-label">主图</text></view><view class="photo-thumb"><image mode="aspectFill" src="/assets/goods/g11.svg" /></view><view class="photo-thumb"><image mode="aspectFill" src="/assets/goods/g13.svg" /></view><view class="photo-thumb"><image mode="aspectFill" src="/assets/goods/g14.svg" /></view><button class="photo-add" data-toast="选择图片" bindtap="handleToast"><image class="icon" mode="aspectFit" src="/assets/icons/camera.svg" /></button></view><view class="section-line-title"><text>图片要求</text></view><view class="process-list"><view class="process-row done"><text class="process-index">1</text><text class="process-main"><text>主图清晰</text><text>建议 1:1 正方形，主体居中，避免文字过多</text></text><text class="status-pill success">已符合</text></view><view class="process-row"><text class="process-index">2</text><text class="process-main"><text>详情图补充</text><text>可展示产地、包装、规格、质检信息</text></text><text class="status-pill info">建议</text></view></view><view class="bottom-actions"><button class="action-btn secondary" data-toast="已设为主图" bindtap="handleToast">设为主图</button><navigator class="action-btn" url="/pages/merchant-design/publish/publish">保存图片</navigator></view>
</view>

<view class="toast {{toastText ? 'show' : ''}}">{{toastText}}</view>
